---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import { BOOK_HREF } from '../../data/nav';
---
<PageLayout section="About" kicker="About" title="Our story" lede="Why we built the midlife care women deserve.">
  <div class="bg-white border border-sand rounded-5xl p-8 lg:p-12 reveal">
    <div class="prose-none text-stone leading-relaxed space-y-4 max-w-2xl">
      <p>Too many women spend years being dismissed during the most disruptive hormonal transition of their lives. We started ResetWell Plus to change that, with clinicians who specialise in midlife health, and care that treats the whole person, not a checklist.</p>
      <p>Our approach is simple: listen first, explain clearly, and offer real, evidence-based solutions so relief comes sooner. No referrals, no insurance maze, just expert care at a transparent price.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8 grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
      <div class="bg-cream rounded-3xl p-6"><p class="font-serif text-3xl text-clay">2024</p><p class="text-sm text-stone mt-1">founded</p></div>
      <div class="bg-cream rounded-3xl p-6"><p class="font-serif text-3xl text-clay">12,000+</p><p class="text-sm text-stone mt-1">women cared for</p></div>
      <div class="bg-cream rounded-3xl p-6"><p class="font-serif text-3xl text-clay">4.9 / 5</p><p class="text-sm text-stone mt-1">average rating</p></div>
    </div>
    <a href={BOOK_HREF} class="mt-8 btn-primary">Book a Consultation</a>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
